{"tid":1098858,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"(物業分配 法律問題) 跪求幫手","createTime":"2019-04-09T11:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T05:40:38.000Z","uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb5296a64ae51d219ee6d3b54e52addddfab691","tid":1098858,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:22:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的, E個POST係幫個FD開既, 條柒頭冇AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有幫佢問, 睇下有巴打可以指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係我個FD既情況:<br />\n我FD: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我FD個家姐: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=======================<br />\n就咁既, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />移民左去澳洲，係專業人士+有澳洲居留權，而<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係香港人。<br />\n<br />\n近期屋企諗住係澳洲買二手樓，希望過幾年(target 大約5年左右)有水位就放返岀去，賺到既就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對分  做各自既首期。<br />\n<br />\n雖然屋企主力俾, 但都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊借loan幫手供先夠做，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦要俾自己d saving 幫補，所以扣除父幹，大約要出三分二。<br />\n<br />\n但因為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇澳洲國籍，屋契如果要落埋佢名既話就要額外俾好多稅同埋要搞好多麻煩野，初步諗住淨係落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />名先，但佢屋企同時又想保障返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，令層樓既業權唔會100%歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所有，佢地想白紙黑字有簽名，廢事第日嘈到家破人亡反晒面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n所以想知<br />\n<ins><strong>有無d咩方法 (例如搵律師簽份附加條款??)，係講明第日層樓如果賣左岀去， <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仍然可以合法地分一半，可以保障到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ </strong></ins> <br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49a83f2099f479e303af9475d6a3a85fcdf48cf","tid":1098858,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"38c6ecc9c7bea06fe7d61230d9b943f41e8014b3","tid":1098858,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"22"},{"pid":"5cdd6d45ed3b7cb1192604dd7addd03d6f6416e9","tid":1098858,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"333"},{"pid":"d48db8134a980df94527c161a9fb7bf24f21fd37","tid":1098858,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2064d66d421e973de322add3032b27cc4ac756fc","tid":1098858,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e28f35bc8265bc51feeb0d062f1ba18ae8d474b","tid":1098858,"uid":66254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:03:31.000Z","msg":"開公司?"},{"pid":"db1a85950cea4e4a0349ed4484f4c9bbf55f2ef5","tid":1098858,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"法律問題唔搵律師，幾百幾千萬既野信連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37